'short_description' => '<p>The MacBook Pro 14-inch with M3 chip delivers groundbreaking performance in a compact form factor, with hardware-accelerated ray tracing, a stunning Liquid Retina XDR ProMotion display, and up to 22 hours of battery life. Three Thunderbolt 4 ports, HDMI 2.1, and an SDXC slot provide comprehensive connectivity, while the six-speaker Spatial Audio system and 1080p camera ensure excellent media and communication experiences. Available in Space Black and Silver finishes with up to 24GB unified memory.</p>',
