'sony-wh-1000xm5' => [
'content' => '<p>The Sony WH-1000XM5 wireless headphones define the gold standard for active noise cancellation, delivering an immersive listening experience that effectively silences the outside world whether you are commuting, working in a busy office, or traveling internationally. Eight microphones combined with two dedicated processors — the HD Noise Cancelling Processor QN1 and the Integrated Processor V1 — create Sony\'s most sophisticated noise cancellation system ever developed, automatically adapting to your environment in real time.</p>
