<p>Speak-to-Chat technology automatically detects your voice and pauses music instantly when you start speaking, resuming playback when your conversation ends. Quick Attention mode lets you cup your hand over the right earcup to temporarily pass through environmental audio for brief conversations without removing the headphones. Multipoint connection allows simultaneous pairing with two devices, switching seamlessly between your phone and laptop.</p>
<p>Call quality is exceptional thanks to four beamforming microphones and precise voice pickup technology that isolates your voice from background noise for crystal-clear calls and video conferencing. The 30-hour battery life with ANC enabled means you can listen for days between charges, and a quick 3-minute charge provides 3 hours of playback when you are running low.</p>
<p>The redesigned lightweight construction with soft earpads ensures extended wearing comfort during long listening sessions. Touch controls on the right earcup allow intuitive volume, playback, and call management. The Sony Headphones Connect app provides deep customization of EQ settings, noise cancellation levels, and personalized sound profiles based on your hearing profile.</p>',
'short_description' => '<p>The Sony WH-1000XM5 delivers industry-leading active noise cancellation through eight microphones and dual processors, combined with exceptional Hi-Res Audio via LDAC codec. Thirty hours of battery life, Speak-to-Chat automatic pause, multipoint dual-device connection, and crystal-clear call quality make these the complete wireless headphone package. Lightweight construction with premium soft earpads ensures all-day comfort, while the Sony Headphones Connect app enables deep personalization of sound and ANC settings.</p>',
],

'apple-airpods-pro-gen-3' => [
'content' => '<p>The Apple AirPods Pro 3rd Generation represent the most sophisticated audio product Apple has ever created for the ears, delivering a transformative listening experience through advanced hardware and intelligent software working in perfect harmony. The H2 chip enables next-generation Active Noise Cancellation that is twice as effective as the previous generation, creating a quiet personal space even in the most noisy and chaotic environments including airplanes, busy streets, and crowded offices.</p>
<p>Adaptive Audio is an entirely new listening mode that dynamically blends Active Noise Cancellation and Transparency mode based on your surroundings. When you walk through a quiet space, Adaptive Audio lets more environmental sound through for situational awareness. When noise increases, it smoothly increases cancellation to keep you focused. Conversation Awareness automatically reduces volume and enhances voices when you begin speaking, making natural conversations effortless.</p>
<p>Sound quality has been substantially improved with a new custom driver and amplifier. The low-distortion audio at all frequencies means music sounds more natural and detailed, with precise spatial imaging through Personalized Spatial Audio with dynamic head tracking. The system uses your iPhone\'s TrueDepth camera to create a personal acoustic profile that maps audio precisely to your unique ear shape.</p>
<p>The MagSafe charging case provides full protection and delivers up to 30 hours of total listening time including six hours in the earbuds themselves. The case charges wirelessly via MagSafe, Qi, and Apple Watch chargers, and includes a Lightning connector for wired charging. Precision Finding uses Ultra Wideband technology to locate the case\'s exact position when misplaced.</p>
<p>The customizable touch controls on the stem allow intuitive management of playback, calls, and ANC modes. IP54 water and dust resistance protects both the earbuds and case from sweat and splashes during workouts. Instant pairing and automatic device switching across all your Apple devices make the AirPods Pro 3rd Gen the seamless choice for the Apple ecosystem.</p>',
'short_description' => '<p>AirPods Pro 3rd Generation features the H2 chip delivering Active Noise Cancellation twice as powerful as before, alongside the new Adaptive Audio mode that intelligently blends ANC and Transparency based on your environment. Conversation Awareness, Personalized Spatial Audio with head tracking, and 30 hours total battery life with the MagSafe charging case make these the ultimate earbuds for Apple users. IP54 resistance, Precision Finding, and seamless ecosystem switching complete the package.</p>',
],

'anker-7-in-1-usb-c-hub' => [
'content' => '<p>The Anker 7-in-1 USB-C Hub is an essential productivity tool for anyone working with a modern laptop, instantly transforming a single USB-C port into a complete workstation connectivity hub. Designed with both power users and everyday professionals in mind, this compact hub delivers reliable, high-speed connectivity without the bulk or complexity of larger docking stations, fitting easily into a pocket or laptop bag for use anywhere.</p>
<p>The 4K HDMI port supports video output at 4K resolution and 30Hz refresh rate, enabling crisp external monitor connections for presentations, extended desktop setups, or mirroring your display in meeting rooms and conference spaces. For content creators and photographers, the SD and TF card reader slots provide fast simultaneous access to camera memory cards, eliminating the need to carry separate card readers.</p>
<p>Three USB-A 3.0 ports deliver 5Gbps data transfer speeds for fast file transfers from external drives, connection of USB peripherals including keyboards, mice, and external storage devices, and charging of smartphones and tablets. The pass-through USB-C Power Delivery port supports up to 100W charging, ensuring your laptop charges at full speed through the hub without requiring a separate power adapter.</p>
<p>Anker\'s advanced temperature management system prevents overheating during extended use, while built-in surge protection safeguards your connected devices from power fluctuations. The plug-and-play design requires no drivers or software installation — simply connect the hub to your laptop\'s USB-C port and all seven ports become immediately available.</p>
<p>Bus-powered operation means no external power supply is needed, keeping your workspace clean and clutter-free. The compact aluminum housing measures just 11cm in length and weighs 66 grams, making it genuinely portable. Compatible with MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, iPad Pro, Dell XPS, Surface Pro, and any USB-C Windows laptop. An 18-month warranty and Anker\'s renowned customer support provide peace of mind.</p>',
'short_description' => '<p>The Anker 7-in-1 USB-C Hub instantly expands a single USB-C port into seven essential connections: 4K HDMI output, three USB-A 3.0 ports for 5Gbps transfers, SD and TF card reader slots, and a 100W USB-C Power Delivery pass-through port. Bus-powered and driver-free, this compact 66g aluminum hub works with any USB-C laptop including MacBook, iPad Pro, Dell XPS, and Surface. Built-in surge protection and Anker\'s 18-month warranty ensure reliable, safe connectivity anywhere.</p>',
],

